{"id": "1513067831204515902", "channel_id": "1505167541818101862", "type": 0, "author_id": "594196021119287316", "author_name": "nemu_s_t_a_r", "author_bot": false, "content": "王藍桐食兔子\n王藍桐性快，嘗食兔子，以劍刺之，不得，便大怒，舉以擲地；兔子於地躍起逃離，仍下地以飛刃擲之，又不得，瞋甚；復十秒使星爆中，斬死即棄之。克利夫聞而大笑，曰：「使閃光有此性，猶當無一豪可論，況藍桐耶？」", "timestamp": "2026-06-07T06:31:22.400000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513067830856384622", "filename": "2lnLrTq.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 224818, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1505167541818101862/1513067830856384622/2lnLrTq.png?ex=6a270a7a&is=6a25b8fa&hm=bb9607923ef055a85f50a8c7ab439ace68cc37ae354f50361c6bc001cc285a5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1505167541818101862", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
